title: Binaerpilot - Robot Wars  {by marvin_snemand}
description:
An album by the Norwegian "robot" Binaerpilot.


He makes electronic music and puts it out on the internet - and calls on others to do it too - for free downloading.

That&#039;s why I decided to put out his music on The Pirate Bay (and because I like it...)


Year: 2007
Genre: Electronic
Total time: 27 minutes
Bitrate: 128 kbps

Track Listing:


1. Tokyomatrix 3000 - 4:45
2. Smile (Make Your Body Move) - 4:18
